p:
The title compound is prepared in a manner analogous to the procedure set forth in Method DII from 3-(4-bromo-phenyl)-4,5-dicyano-1-methyl-1H-pyrrole-2-carboxylic acid ethyl ester (prepared in example E-267) and the corresponding aryl boronate. Mass spectrum (m/e): 402.1 (M+1). R
f = 0.4 (50% Et 2O in hexanes).
